#18. Eclipse + Tomcat


$ cd /usr/share/tomcat8
$ sudo ln -s /var/lib/tomcat8/conf conf
$ sudo ln -s /etc/tomcat8/policy.d/03catalina.policy conf/catalina.policy
$ sudo ln -s /var/log/tomcat8 log
$ sudo chmod -R 777 conf

Window > Preferences > Server > Runtime Environment > Add
Name: Apache Tomcat v8.5
Tomcat installation directory: /usr/share/tomcat8
